1. Kanishcheva, O. (2026). *ParlLangID-UA-RU: A Model for Language Identification in Code-Switched Ukrainian-Russian Contexts*. Hugging Face Repository. https://huggingface.co/OKanishcheva/ParlLangID-UA-RU

