3. Conneau, A., Khandelwal, K., Goyal, N., et al. (2019). *Unsupervised Cross-lingual Representation Learning at Scale*. arXiv:1911.02116.

4. Unidive WG1. (2024). *Creation of a Token-Level Language Identification Dataset for Ukrainian-Russian Code-Switching*. Presentation material, 2nd Unidive General Meeting. https://unidive.lisn.upsaclay.fr/lib/exe/fetch.php?media=meetings:general_meetings:2nd_unidive_general_meeting:48_creation_dataset_of_token_lang.pdf

5. Labelbox, Inc. (2026). *Labelbox: Data labeling platform for training AI*. https://app.labelbox.com

6. Brown University Research Group. (2026). *NLP-UK: Natural Language Processing for Ukrainian*. https://github.com/brown-uk/nlp_uk
